text.section:
Unless authorized to practice audiology under this title or unless otherwise provided for in this article, a person may not use, with the intent to represent that the person practices audiology, words or terms, including:
"Audiological";
"Audiologist";
"Audiology";
"Aural rehabilitation";
"Hearing clinic";
"Hearing clinician";
"Hearing rehabilitation"; or
"Hearing specialist".
